1. Place 2 tablespoons diced fruit, 1 tablespoon citrus fruit, and some herb leaves in a glass. 2. Crush with a spoon or muddler. 3. Add 2 tablespoons syrup, or to taste. 4. Fill glass with crushed ice. 5. Mix in spirits. 6. Top with sparkling water or club soda. Pineapple, lemon, mint, citrus syrup, vodka Mango, lime, ginger syrup, gin Watermelon, orange, rum Kiwi, grapefruit, tequila